- Understand the responsible AI principles for implementation, ethical considerations, and how to mitigate risks.

- Based on identified risks, learn how to implement key security tooling for language models.


AI development and deployment are ETA (ethical, transparent and accountable). Databricks helps to monitor, manage and fine-tune LLM. Responsible AI involves detecting bias, following data privacy rules. 
AI principles throughout LLM lifecycle, AI systems to align with societal values and regulations while getting the most out of these advanced models.

https://microsoftlearning.github.io/mslearn-databricks/Instructions/Exercises/AI-06-Responsible-AI.html

